\id 2JN - Sembeleke Samberigi PNG 2 John 12/2/91 Macnaughtan
\h 2 DIONI
\toc1 Dionimaęž‰ yaapo peao tapaeyeke wapee
\toc2 2 Dioni
\toc3 2 Dioni
\mt1 Dionimaęž‰ yaapo peao tapaeyeke wapee
\c 1
\p 
\v 1 IĚ±taęž‰ you halimaęž‰ mo hande yaka pukimaęž‰ homolo ankulaęž‰ ankulaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ do tameiyaęž‰ tapaasome. IĚ±maęž‰ homeke diaęž‰yaęž‰laęž‰pate mo hande otaęž‰eki hone ulaęž‰ wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ make iki pukimaęž‰ homelememe.
\v 2 Pa ekipeke mo hande otaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ niki paęž‰taęž‰ u pelia halaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ wetepe ninaęž‰ make niki ameĚ±leĚ± pa u halieke.
\p 
\v 3 Nikaęž‰ Apaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ make mo Apaęž‰naęž‰ Eiyeke Yesu Ketiso ipiliki telipunaęž‰maęž‰ aęž‰taęž‰maęž‰ homolo tambaęž‰ minaęž‰laęž‰eki make pa hameke aęž‰taęž‰maęž‰ homaęž‰laęž‰eki make puki lopaęž‰niaasaęž‰eki make niki paęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰eki pitaęž‰ pukimaęž‰ homaęž‰laęž‰eki yaapo paęž‰taęž‰ yamaęž‰ kinaęž‰e.
\s1 Otaęž‰eki pitaęž‰ pukimaęž‰ homaęž‰laęž‰eki
\p 
\v 4 Nakaęž‰ mandane weki wandikitaęž‰ mo hande Apaęž‰maęž‰ niki paęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ piaęž‰paęž‰peke laęž‰laęž‰ tupaęž‰ otaęž‰eki paęž‰taęž‰ halemeeki handaęž‰ u hao IĚ±taęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰ tiekemaęž‰ homoaęž‰me.
\v 5 Koto ekinaęž‰ mo wandaęž‰o niki paeyaomaęž‰ pukimaęž‰ homaęž‰ alu alu pumanaęž‰e laa alome. Do wape laaso hataęž‰ neke paęž‰taęž‰ alo pitaęž‰ panake pi ulaęž‰eki diaęž‰yaęž‰laęž‰pate hande ambaęž‰ titinaęž‰ kini pitolo hataęž‰ wia halomaęž‰ pi ulaęž‰eki konee.
\v 6 Do IĚ±maęž‰ alo pukimaęž‰ homaęž‰laęž‰ ekinaęž‰ teketaęž‰ nikanaęž‰maęž‰ otaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ pi ulaęž‰eki oto paęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ hamanaęž‰e laa loaęž‰me. Mo hande titinaęž‰ pi ulaęž‰eki opeleme ekitaęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo pukimaęž‰ homaęž‰laęž‰eki paęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ hapaęž‰peke laęž‰laęž‰eki opelememe.
\p 
\v 7 Mo Yesu Ketisotaęž‰ otaęž‰ kenke hali epeekeme laa hone na wilimi makeaaso hali wopu do kenke honiki honiki pominelememe. Kutupiki some aęž‰ndaęž‰taęž‰ makeaaso hali make Ketisonaęž‰ aęž‰ndaęž‰ tunkuliki halie.
\v 8 Koto ekinaęž‰ leke leke lo hapaęž‰peke. Pa ekipeke mo hande mulueke laa e pokeleme ekitaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ na alupaake pa anaęž‰naęž‰ kone miomenaęž‰ yeke loaęž‰me.
\p 
\v 9 Maęž‰ndaęž‰ epimaęž‰ Ketisomaęž‰ waleekeeki paęž‰taęž‰ na hake pa ankulao mo pate leke peaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ Kodaęž‰taęž‰ koto some yaapo na halaęž‰me. Pate epimaęž‰ mo walaęž‰laęž‰eki paęž‰taęž‰ hayaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ Aęž‰taalaęž‰taęž‰ koto some paęž‰taęž‰ halepeme.
\v 10 Koto ekinaęž‰taęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ epimaęž‰ dupiki walaęž‰laęž‰eki na mea epeaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ koto sometaęž‰ ikaęž‰ da paęž‰taęž‰manu na handaęž‰ meaęž‰paęž‰peke. Kutupa ipiki paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ Puki lopaęž‰niaasaęž‰eki neke paęž‰taęž‰ winaęž‰e pi na lapaęž‰peke.
\v 11 Pa ekipeke maęž‰ndaęž‰ epimaęž‰ koto some paęž‰taęž‰ Puki lopaęž‰niaasaęž‰eki neke paęž‰taęž‰ winaęž‰e leaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ koto some ipikitaęž‰ mo halimaęž‰ pu halaęž‰ hoke hau manunaęž‰ yankeke halaęž‰me.
\s1 Paeyaaso pimanu
\p 
\v 12 IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ la kiaęž‰peke pitaęž‰ wopu ulaęž‰pate mo wape laapeke tameiyaęž‰ pitaęž‰ wape laasaęž‰ tanu yaapotaęž‰ paaso hataęž‰ yaka honemaęž‰taęž‰ IĚ± aęž‰pa iki ameĚ±leĚ± pitaęž‰ pimanu lomanaęž‰e. Pa ekipeke niki paeyao taęž‰naęž‰ tieke pulu paęž‰laęž‰ tupaęž‰ loaęž‰me.
\p 
\v 13 Kutupa nakaęž‰ asinaęž‰ weki wandikimaęž‰taęž‰ ikaęž‰ aęž‰talo pimanu tapaasememe. 
